rg/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many famous faces have reacted to his defeat and taken to social media to thank Andy for his remarkable career.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tennis star has previously won the Gold medal for Team GB in London 2012 and Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999680701444018, \"rank\": 3.188447930268384e-05, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radio 1 presenter Greg James tweeted: \\\"It's going to be awful having to watch tennis and not feel sick to your stomach is not it.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_1\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1127342008276064e-25, \"text\": \"Radio 1\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_1\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank youAndy Murray- it's been, at times, a complete f*****g nightmare but I would not change any of it.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not even want to debate it, he's our greatest ever sportsperson.\\\"\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prime MinisterKeir Starmerpenned: \\\"1 Davis Cup, 2 Olympic golds and 3 Grand Slams.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But more than that, thanks @andy_murray for two decades of phenomenal entertainment and sportsmanship.\\\"\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Clare Balding bursts into tears on BBC after Andy Murray's retirement confirmed    Comedian Dara \\u00d3 Briain also said: \\\"Sad to see @andy_murray finish playing, after a brilliant career.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9972605584600033, \"rank\": 0.002746955655333782, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.196189738275879e-58, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_\\u00d3_Briain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dara \\u00d3 Briain\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_\\u00d3_Briain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_\\u00d3_Briain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last of the Mock The Week gang, this is the final hurrah for us all.\\\"\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"London mayor Sadiq Khan commented on X: \\\"Andy Murray until the end.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1360, \"end\": 1366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_GAA\", \"score\": 0.5513047829789092, \"rank\": 0.8138455561961405, \