t guy off the court, absolute warrior on it.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will miss him, though our nails will not.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks for all the incredible memories Andy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2024 Wimbledon championCarlos Alcarazsaid: \\\"It was a privilege to share the court with you, Andy!\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations on a legendary career and for being an example to all.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You will always have a fan here!\\\"\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Scottish superstar confirmed that the Paris 2024 Olympics would be his final appearance before retiring from professional tennis.\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.9988099833451041, \"rank\": 0.0009458269996636565, \"text\": \"Scottish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2114, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Piers Morgan (@piersmorgan)  Do not miss:Olympics chiefs issue strong statement after Khelif's boxing win sparks row  Do not miss:Andy Murray bursts into tears with Evans after iconic Brit retires at Olympics  Do not miss:Rafael Nadal outlines plans after Olympics fairytale dashed ahead of retirement  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to a